# ryy_pi8 — e^{i(π/8)Y⊗Y}, 기저 B=S·H(Z→Y). plan=봉인 sdg_gate·h_gate·rzz_pi8·s_gate, no MatrixGate. golden=closed-form Pauli 지수.
```json id=app_meta
{"id": "ryy_pi8", "n_sys": 2, "n_anc": 0}
