```python id=app_golden
import numpy as np
Y = np.array([[0,-1j],[1j,0]],complex); YY = np.kron(Y, Y)
golden = (np.cos(np.pi/8)*np.eye(4) + 1j*np.sin(np.pi/8)*YY).astype(complex)
```
